         <abstract id="aspace_f10f234726e41f5efc02b22b7e87b436">Correspondence, autographs, playbills, notebooks, and writings relating to the American theater and the history of theater in New Haven, Connecticut, as collected by Jack Crawford, Mary Hamlin and others.</abstract>
